往往导致支流浮游植物结构及种类差异较大。因此，针对不同区域的主要污染物种类和水文、水动力条件，采取更具有针对性的水华预测与防控措施十分必要。</p></sec><sec id="s7"><title>文章引用</title><p>潘海峰,于洪贤,马成学,柴方营,于 婷,鞠永富. 三江自然保护区5月浮游植物功能群研究及水质评价Study on Phytoplankton Functional Group and Water Quality Evaluation in May of Sanjiang Nature Reserve[J]. 环境保护前沿, 2019, 09(01): 10-16. https://doi.org/10.12677/AEP.2019.91003</p></sec><sec id="s8"><title>参考文献</title></sec></body><back><ref-list><title>References</title><ref id="hanspub.28612-ref1"><label>1</label><mixed-citation publication-type="other" xlink:type="simple">Reynolds, C.S. (2010) Phytoplankton Assemblages and Their Periodicity in Stratifying Lake Systems. Ecography, 3, 141-159. &lt;br&gt;https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1600-0587.1980.tb00721.x</mixed-citation></ref><ref id="hanspub.28612-ref2"><label>2</label><mixed-citation publication-type="other" xlink:type="simple">Grime, J.P. (1977) Evidence for the Existence of Three Primary Strategies in Plants and Its Relevance to Ecological and Evolutionary Theory. American Naturalist, 111, 1169-1194. &lt;br&gt;https://doi.org/10.1086/283244</mixed-citation></ref><ref id="hanspub.28612-ref3"><label>3</label><mixed-citation publication-type="other" xlink:type="simple">崔花淑, 朴正顺, 申晓明, 等. 黑龙江三江保护区的野生动物资源[J]. 野生动物学报, 1999(6): 8-9.</mixed-citation></ref><ref id="hanspub.28612-ref4"><label>4</label><mixed-citation publication-type="other" xlink:type="simple">周洁敏. 对黑龙江三江国家级自然保护区的评价[J]. 林业资源管理, 2001(5): 58-64.</mixed-citation></ref><ref id="hanspub.28612-ref5"><label>5</label><mixed-citation publication-type="other" xlink:type="simple">袁家辉, 孙常乐. 浮游植物评价颍河水质污染研究[J]. 阜阳师范学院学报(自然科学版), 2004, 21(3): 46-49 + 61.</mixed-citation></ref><ref id="hanspub.28612-ref6"><label>6</label><mixed-citation publication-type="other" xlink:type="simple">胡晓红, 陈椽, 李银燕, 向刚, 刘美珊. 以浮游植物评价百花湖水质污染及富营养化[J]. 贵州师范大学学报(自然科学版), 1999(4): 1-7.</mixed-citation></ref><ref id="hanspub.28612-ref7"><label>7</label><mixed-citation publication-type="other" xlink:type="simple">郭沛涌, 林育真, 李玉仙. 东平湖浮游植物与水质评价[J]